General.Name: Euro Kapital Yatirim Ortakligi AS
General.Description: Euro Kapital Yatirim Ortakligi Anonim Sirketi creates and manages partnership portfolio in Turkey. It monitors developments in financial markets, institutions, and partnerships; and offers portfolio management services, as well as conducts research to protect and enhance value of the portfolio. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Ankara, Turkey.
